# Text to Image Generation Specifications

## Font Configuration
- Font: Murecho Bold (Weight 700)
- Source: `@fontsource/murecho` package
- Size: 18px

## Layout Specifications
- Characters per line: 18
- Character width: 18px
- Line height: 40px (1.2x font size)
- Margins: 36px (all sides)

## Color Scheme
- Default text: Black (#000000)
- Hint text: Red (#FF0000)
- Answer text: Blue (#0000FF)
- Background: White (#FFFFFF)

## Implementation File
Main implementation in [text-to-image-tool.ts](mdc:src/mastra/tools/text-to-image-tool.ts)

## Dependencies
Required in [package.json](mdc:package.json):
- `@fontsource/murecho`
- `canvas`

